fulltitle: TANGO on Air with Tango en vivo – Danzarín
title: TANGO on Air with Tango en vivo – Danzarín

description:
The Maestros of Bari Tango Congress 2017 dance “Danzarín” played live by Tango En Vivo during the show TANGO on Air in Bari, Italy.

The Maestros are
Mariana Montes and Sebastian Arce
Roxana Suarez and Sebastian Achaval
Vanesa Villalba and Facundo Pinero
Maria Ines Bogado and Jorge Lopez
Ravena Abdyli and Matteo Antonietti
Giorgia Rossello and Vito Raffanelli
